message.body: Good morning. I hope you're well. How's your week looking?
Hopefully it involves some gainful employment! Got some small side work lined up but still waiting on that call from the union hall. Otherwise just some
volunteering, helping friends out with some stuff, & putzing around the house. Quite an extended staycation i'm getting, huh? How about you?
Also doing a bunch of side work. Better to be busy than broke I suppose
I generally find myself with enough money or enough time but usually not both @ once. I suppose thats why youre a commie, huh?
Lol! I'm also a big fan of the 4 hour day when possible!
How did your day shape up? Mine was busy- work, then took a walk with a friend, then a focus group. Now i'm about to go on a bike ride
